name: About Page
description: A page on your website where users can learn more about you and what you do.

name: Contact Page
description: A page on your website where users can get in touch with you.

name: FAQ Page
description: A page on your website which addresses common concerns, questions and objections that users may have.

name: Press Page
description: A page on your website with information that the media and press would find useful.

name: Terms Page
description: A page on your website with the terms and conditions to which users must agree in order to use or access your website.

name: Testimonials Page
description: A page on your website which contains awards, certifications and customer reviews.
